396
00:23:27.792 --> 00:23:31.632
Two were tested negative and one was tested positive.

397
00:23:32.052 --> 00:23:34.932
He had an early diagnosis and a more

398
00:23:35.012 --> 00:23:38.612
severe polyposis as compared to his mother.

399
00:23:41.632 --> 00:23:45.612
Mosaicism of APC was found to be associated with

400
00:23:45.672 --> 00:23:48.732
a younger age and a higher adenoma burden.

401
00:23:49.932 --> 00:23:53.032
The proportion of patients that were

402
00:23:55.152 --> 00:23:58.812
diagnosed early was greater in mosaic patient

403
00:23:59.052 --> 00:24:02.692
as compared to non-mosaic patients, with a median age of

404
00:24:02.752 --> 00:24:06.592
45 years as compared to 53 for the non-mosaic

405
00:24:06.652 --> 00:24:10.496
cases.The same was observed

406
00:24:10.596 --> 00:24:14.136
for adenoma burden. The proportion of patients with

407
00:24:14.536 --> 00:24:18.176
a larger number of polyps was higher in mosaic

408
00:24:18.216 --> 00:24:22.016
patients as compared to non-mosaic patients, with a higher number

409
00:24:22.836 --> 00:24:25.916
significantly shown as here.

410
00:24:28.896 --> 00:24:32.736
What we saw as well is that the pathogenic variants

411
00:24:32.776 --> 00:24:34.456
that we had were

412
00:24:35.896 --> 00:24:39.716
often fitting the colibactin signature that

413
00:24:39.776 --> 00:24:41.516
is described in

414
00:24:42.236 --> 00:24:46.156
colon cancer. And I

415
00:24:46.216 --> 00:24:50.176
summarized here all

416
00:24:50.246 --> 00:24:54.156
polyps for all patients. The dark boxes

417
00:24:54.396 --> 00:24:57.496
are the lesions that were

418
00:24:57.936 --> 00:25:01.896
