420
00:25:04.996 --> 00:25:07.196
When we looked at the whole series,

421
00:25:08.416 --> 00:25:10.376
40% of the patients

422
00:25:11.196 --> 00:25:14.136
had a sign of colibactin exposure

423
00:25:15.216 --> 00:25:15.976
in their genome.

424
00:25:18.256 --> 00:25:22.056
In parallel, we investigated whether we could find the

425
00:25:22.116 --> 00:25:25.956
