431
00:25:45.296 --> 00:25:48.656
any strict correlation concordance

432
00:25:48.736 --> 00:25:51.906
between the genomic imprinting and the presence of the

433
00:25:52.016 --> 00:25:55.476
genotoxic bacteria, we were able to

434
00:25:55.576 --> 00:25:58.956
