00:44:33.955 --> 00:44:37.176
get at that exact point. The quality was

760
00:44:37.236 --> 00:44:40.996
not very good from the section, so we

761
00:44:41.396 --> 00:44:43.096
had a really hard time identifying the SNPs.

762
00:44:43.156 --> 00:44:43.756
We were able to

763
00:44:45.516 --> 00:44:49.496
make ancestry calls, but we weren't

764
00:44:49.556 --> 00:44:51.676
super confident in much more than that.

765
00:44:52.696 --> 00:44:56.676
So that is something we're interested in following up on, yeah.

766
00:44:59.516 --> 00:45:03.216
Great presentation. So from a breast oncologist, a quick question.

767
00:45:03.956 --> 00:45:06.236
Have you looked at within the Black women,

768
00:45:07.156 --> 00:45:10.816
young versus old age? There's some work that we have

769
