01:14:18.154 --> 01:14:22.084
agnostic of molecular subtypes, and thus far, we have seen that

1251
01:14:22.134 --> 01:14:22.454
signal

1252
01:14:23.314 --> 01:14:24.934
in the biobank samples. But,

1253
01:14:26.094 --> 01:14:29.534
of course, it's too early to consider that without

