1255
01:14:32.994 --> 01:14:36.514
agnostic of the subtype, either by ductal or

1256
01:14:36.614 --> 01:14:39.334
lobular and also by molecular subtype.

1257
01:14:39.394 --> 01:14:41.234
We do expect this to be a test for all.

1258
01:14:41.594 --> 01:14:43.634
And then just a super quick follow-up question.

1259
01:14:43.714 --> 01:14:43.724
Yeah.

1260
01:14:43.734 --> 01:14:47.134
Based off of the 80% detection rate that you found for

1261
01:14:49.594 --> 01:14:52.914
the early stage one and stage two tumors, was there any

1262
01:14:53.474 --> 01:14:55.174
